Welcome to Arthur Andersen's U.S. Accounting Research Manager.
You now have full access to this comprehensive database for a full year.  We are
pleased to service your financial reporting needs.

HOW TO ACCESS:
The Internet address for the U.S. Accounting Research Manager site is:
http://www.arm.arthurandersen.com  NOTE: for recent Trial users, this is a
different address than the 30-day trial site

To access U.S. Accounting Research Manager according to the option you selected:

INTERNET ONLY SUBSCRIBERS
This provides access to a real-time comprehensive database via the Internet.

1. Enter the above address into your browser and set as a FAVORITE. For recent
trial users, if you set the trial site as a FAVORITE, please be sure to re-set
the above address.

2. Click on ACCESS TO ACCOUNTING RESEARCH MANAGER FOR INTERNET SUBSCRIBER.

3. You will be prompted for your user name (featured below) and password (to be
sent in a separate e-mail).  For recent trial users, your trial user name and
password are identical to your full subscription user name and password.

4. You will then see the opening page of the U.S. Accounting Research Manager.

TIPS & REMINDERS

HOW TO USE U.S. ACCOUNTING RESEARCH MANAGER
To better familiarize you with this tool and maximize your time, we suggest when
you first visit the site to access the link FOR ASSISTANCE GETTING STARTED,
CLICK HERE NOW in the lower left hand corner of the navigator pane.

This will guide you through:
- Overview
- Tutorial: How to Use Research Manager
- Tips
- Support tools
- FAQ (commonly asked questions and answers)
- Glossary

